istration forms</li><li>Proactive chat invitations</li><li>Multiple chats</li><li>Intuitive native chatbot (Chat Butler)</li><li>Automatic translator for seven languages</li><li>Offline messages</li><li>Service time and rating settings</li><li>Real-time visitor and event analytics</li><li>Integration with chat analytics, social networks, and other apps, including Slack, Facebook Messenger, Asana, Pipedrive, Telegram, and Help Scout</li><li>Optimized for mobile</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for:</strong> Businesses that use apps like Slack or Asana.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/userlike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Userlike</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>16. Chatra Live Chat</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins chatra live chat chatbot plugin\" class=\"wp-image-614698\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chatra-live-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chatra Live Chat</a> is a free WordPress live chat plugin that provides a trustworthy environment to convert your website guests to customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Chatra Live Chat saves your cart and increases your sales by empowering you to contact visitors on the checkout page proactively. This gives you a chance to guide your customers and attend to their concerns and questions.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Chatra Live Chat</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Simple interface</li><li>Unlimited concurrent conversations</li><li>Offline messages and group chats</li><li>Typing insights and typo corrections</li><li>Agent photos available pre-chat</li><li>Real-time visitor analytics</li><li>Advanced trigger option</li><li>Intelligent form bot for custom contact forms</li><li>Integration with email marketing services, Facebook, and e-commerce platforms such as WooCommerce</li><li>Mobile application available</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for: </strong>Businesses proactive in converting customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chatra-live-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Chatra Live Chat</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Final Thoughts: The Top 16 Free WordPress Live Chat Support Plugins</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/marketing-statistics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">over half of businesses online</a> claiming lead generation is their greatest <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/what-is-marketing\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">marketing</a> challenge, you need effective solutions to stand out amongst the competition.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress live chat plugins are effective not just for lead generation but also for better conversions, sales, <a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/service/customer-acquisition\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">customer acquisition</a>, and support.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Regardless of the size or type of business you do, WordPress live chat plugins will work if you choose your companys most suitable solution from the list of free WordPress live chat plugins above.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready for more qualified leads and website experience? Get started with <a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/pricing/marketing\" rel=\"no